    "name": "Square Fishing Builder",
    "steam_appid": 3133140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>每次独特的游戏</strong><br>游戏具有随机地图系统，每次新游戏都会生成各种类型的树木、岩石、灌木和动物，每个都有其特定的属性，使每次游戏都独一无二。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>建造</strong><br>游戏中有各种类型的建筑物，从房屋、捕鱼陷阱、围栏和种植园到不同类型的地板。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>种植园</strong><br>提供各种类型的种植园。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>面对环境</strong><br>游戏有天气变化，会影响玩家的游戏体验，例如下雨。此外，还有野生动物可能会伤害村庄，从狼到鸟。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>全新的RTS系统</strong><br>游戏具有全新的村民控制系统，玩家不直接控制村民，而是只选择要收集的资源类型。村民有自主选择收集资源的能力，使游戏更加动态。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>捕鱼、捕鱼和更多的捕鱼！</strong><br>游戏提供100种不同的鱼类供玩家捕捉！",
